overview: The user wanted to improve the aesthetics of their sleep questionnaire
  app, which they felt was too generic. The agent initiated a comprehensive
  review of the app's visual design, identifying areas such as the color
  palette, typography, spacing, form elements, and overall visual interest that
  needed refinement. The approach involved replacing the existing corporate-like
  blue/indigo scheme with a calming, sleep-themed palette of deep indigos,
  purples, and soft teals. Key decisions included revamping the main
   layout, enhancing the progress bar, and transforming the
   into a more visually appealing welcome experience.
  Additionally, individual UI components like checkboxes, sliders, and radio
  groups were restyled to align with the new theme, and section groupings were
  improved for better visual flow. The outcome is a more sophisticated,
  professional, and emotionally resonant interface tailored for a sleep
  assessment experience.
